<section
    id="jornada-laboral"
    class="relative text-[#e7e5e4] font-serif min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center py-12 md:py-24"
>
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 w-full">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <span
                class="trigo-chapter text-amber-600/60 text-xs md:text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase block mb-4"
                >El Coste del Progreso</span
            >
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-[#e7e5e4] mb-6">La Jornada Laboral</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-[#a8a29e] max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                La promesa de la agricultura era la seguridad, pero el precio fue el tiempo libre.
                Contrario a la creencia popular, la vida "primitiva" no era una lucha constante.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-end h-[50vh] md:h-[400px]">
            <!-- Hunter Gatherer Bar -->
            <div class="flex flex-col justify-end h-full group">
                <div
                    class="mb-4 text-center opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"
                >
                    <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-emerald-400">~3-5 horas</span>
                    <p class="text-xs text-emerald-500/60 uppercase tracking-widest mt-1">
                        Subsistencia
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="relative w-full bg-stone-800 rounded-t-lg overflow-hidden h-[35%] transition-all duration-1000 ease-out group-hover:bg-stone-700"
                >
                    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full h-full bg-emerald-900/20"></div>
                    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-emerald-500/50"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="mt-4 text-center">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#e7e5e4]">Cazador-Recolector</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-[#a8a29e] mt-2">
                        Tiempo libre abundante. Trabajo intermitente.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Farmer Bar -->
            <div class="flex flex-col justify-end h-full group">
                <div
                    class="mb-4 text-center opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"
                >
                    <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-amber-500">~9-10 horas</span>
                    <p class="text-xs text-amber-500/60 uppercase tracking-widest mt-1">
                        De sol a sol
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="relative w-full bg-stone-800 rounded-t-lg overflow-hidden h-[90%] transition-all duration-1000 ease-out group-hover:bg-stone-700"
                >
                    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full h-full bg-amber-900/20"></div>
                    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-amber-500/50"></div>
                    <!-- Sweat/Toil pattern overlay -->
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20 mix-blend-overlay"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="mt-4 text-center">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#e7e5e4]">Agricultor Neolítico</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-[#a8a29e] mt-2">
                        Trabajo constante. Preparación de suelo, siembra, cosecha, molienda.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-16 text-center">
            <p class="text-xs text-[#57534e] italic">
                Datos basados en estudios de Marshall Sahlins ("La sociedad opulenta primitiva") y
                registros antropológicos de sociedades !Kung.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
